<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <title>Document</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #F5F7FA;
      padding: 32px;
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }

    span {
      color: #6366F1;
    }

    .unsubscribe {
      color: #6366F1;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    button {
      width: 290px;
      height: 48px;
      padding: 12px 32px;
      border: none;
      color: white;
      background-color: #6366F1;
      border-radius: 3px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-family: 'SF Pro', sans-serif;
    }

    ul {
      line-height: 32px;
    }

    p,
    li {
      color: #46586B;
      font-family: 'SF Pro', sans-serif;
    }

    h3 {
      color: #46586B;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-family: 'SF Pro', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'New York Large', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 32px;
    }

    main {
      background-color: white;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 40px;
      gap: 40px;
      border-radius: 3px;
    }

    .xertis-link {
      display: inline !important;
    }

    .xertis-link a {
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
    }

    .xertis-link p {
      color: #6366F1;
      font-family: 'SF Pro', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      color: #6366F1;
      font-weight: 510;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .xertis-email-content {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 40px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    footer p {
      text-align: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      body {
        padding: 16px;
      }

      main {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      footer {
        padding: 20px;
        align-items: start;
      }

      footer p {
        text-align: start;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <main>
    <div class="xertis-link">
      <a href="client-link" target="_blank">
        <img src="./xertis-email-logo.svg" alt="Xertis logo" class="mb-1">
        <p>Xertis</p>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h1>Welcome to Xertis - Let's Get Started!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="xertis-email-content">
      <p class="m-0">Hi {{username}},</p>
      <div>
        <p>
          Welcome to Xertis! We’re excited to have you join our platform for creating and issuing blockchain-powered
          certificates.
        </p>
        <h3>Here’s a quick guide to help you get started:</h3>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3>Step 1: Complete your profile</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Log in to your account and complete your profile details.
          </li>
          <li>
            Connect your wallet to start issuing certificates
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3>Step 2: Create Your First Certificate</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Click the “Create Certificate” button on your dashboard.
          </li>
          <li>
            Fill in the details, and set a mint price (optional).
          </li>
          <li>
            Generate your minting link and share it with recipients.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3>Step 3: Share and Manage Certificates</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Share the minting link with your recipients
          </li>
          <li>
            Track mints, view transactions and manage your certificates from your dashboard
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-3">Get Started Now:</h3>
        <button>Create Your First Certificate</button>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p>We're here to help you every step of the way. Welcome to the future of certification</p>
        <p>
          Best regards,
          <br>
          The Xertis Team
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p class="lh-base">Questions or concerns? Get in touch with us at <span>xertis.reply@gmail.com</span>
      <br>
      Never miss a beat! Follow us on <span>Twitter</span> , <span>Facebook</span> and <span>Instagram.</span>
    </p>
    <p>Don’t want any more emails from Xertis? <a href="https://xertis-abc.vercel.app" class="unsubscribe"
        target="_blank">Unsubscribe.</a>
  </footer>
</body>

</html>